          <b>Tax Exempt:</b> This invoice will be generated without GST (CGST / SGST / IGST). All tax values are set to zero. Suitable for exempt, nil-rated, zero-rated or non-GST supplies.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tax Summary -->
      <div class="gst-section" style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:#fafafa;">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#111;margin-bottom:14px;">Tax Summary</div>
